divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking my boyfriend to work. I waited for him to lock our door when I looked up and saw over 50 star like ufos traveling North to South past the Taurus Constellation and disappear just past Orions belt. All i could say was "Whoa..." my boyfriend didnt know what was going on he asked me whats wrong and I told him what i saw it only lasted abouy 15 seconds but i was still in shock. just about 2 days before i seen the same type of objects but about 7 or 8 in a V formation. im shocked at this activity im just in awe.
